replies.body:
But you could at least put a piece of news in the beta client, right? I mean, how am I supposed to find out that there even is a rotating game mode in the other client otherwise? Am I supposed to just remember that it's on every weekend when I'm stuck in the preseason-quicksand? if I hadn't decided to check up on the Boards today I wouldn't even have found out that I missed a whole weekend of One for All and also would've missed the next one right after too...
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}} 
not cool, man. not cool at all.
